data.description: This is an amazing opportunity to live in  a great neighbrohood and walk into equity with a little sweat equity. Welcome to 846 Lincoln Ave, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Franklinville, NJ. This property boasts a prime corner lot location, offering a sense of privacy and ample space for outdoor activities. With its unique architectural design, the interior features high ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere, providing an abundance of natural light throughout. The spacious 10-car driveway provides convenient parking for residents and guests. Situated in a highly sought-after neighborhood, this home presents an excellent opportunity for those seeking a peaceful and family-friendly community. Offering endless potential, this property invites you to envision and create your dream living space. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home sweet home!
